---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About The Tech Teacher.">
  <section class="section container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
        <h1 style="max-width:none; font-size:clamp(2.6rem, 6vw, 4.8rem);">A practical education technology notebook</h1>
        <p>
          The Tech Teacher is a personal archive of teaching ideas, digital workflows, classroom experiments, and reflections on technology in education.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="max-width:760px;">
      <p>
        This rebuild keeps the spirit of the original Blogger site while making it faster, easier to maintain, and simpler to host for free. Posts live as Markdown files, so the archive can be edited in any text editor and deployed without a database or paid CMS.
      </p>
      <p>
        Replace this page with your own bio, teaching background, favorite topics, and links to profiles or resources.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
